snippet.title: Donkey Kong Bananza – Nintendo Direct | Nintendo Switch 2
snippet.description:
Donkey Kong Bananza is coming exclusively to Nintendo Switch 2 on July 17, 2025! Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/us/gaming-systems/switch-2/featured-games/donkey-kong-bananza/?utm_source=HW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=S1001-01&utm_id=S1001-01

Explore a vast underground world—by smashing your way through it! Bash, throw, and climb through just about anything in DK’s brand-new 3D platforming action-adventure game!

#NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch2 #DonkeyKongBananza

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
